
Breeding simulation for testing ancestoral haplotype inference algorithms

1) sim.py -> data/recombs_rand-mating_r<rate>_g<gen>.log
          -> data/recombs_sib-mating_r<rate>_g<gen>.log
          -> data/recombs_full-mating_r<rate>_g<gen>.log (combined random and sibling mating)

2) haplotype_desc.py -> data/desc_seq.nuc
                     -> data/desc_segments.bed

3) call_SNPs.py -> data/sim_SNPs.bed

